OL,3,CGovernment to run AquaSplash leisure
OL,4,Ccentre amid 'rising costs'
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey will take
OL,7,Fdirect control over the AquaSplash
OL,8,Fleisure centre.
OL,10,FIt will come under the Active
OL,11,Fprogramme, which already runs four
OL,12,Fother swimming pools across the island.
OL,14,FThe facility is currently run by Serco
OL,15,FJersey Limited, but a change was
OL,16,Fagreed after a review of how to
OL,17,F"efficiently operate" the site.
