OL,3,CGovernment to run AquaSplash leisure
OL,4,Ccentre amid 'rising costs'
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Government said:
OL,7,F"The change is being made to give the
OL,8,FGovernment greater control in managing
OL,9,Frising costs across the island and
OL,10,Fstreamline services with the other
OL,11,Ffacilities managed by Active."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Serco added: "We
OL,14,Fare disappointed to be leaving
OL,15,FAquaSplash after almost 25 successful
OL,16,Fyears in Jersey, yet fully understand
OL,17,Fthe need for the Government to deliver
OL,18,Foperational efficiencies in its
OL,19,Fleisure facilities.
