OL,4,Ccentre amid 'rising costs'
OL,6,F"We are very proud of our achievements
OL,7,Fover this time in improving the health
OL,8,Fand wellbeing of the local communities
OL,9,Fand will continue to work in
OL,10,Fpartnership with the Government of
OL,11,FJersey for a smooth transition in
OL,12,F2026."
OL,14,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister,
OL,15,FConstable Andy Jehan, explained: "This
OL,16,Fchange will deliver better value for
OL,17,Ftaxpayers and ensure that the
OL,18,FAquaSplash can continue to operate as
OL,19,Fnormal and serve the public.
