OL,4,Ccentre amid 'rising costs'
OL,6,F"We know this news may be worrying for
OL,7,FAquaSplash staff, and we want to
OL,8,Freassure them that we're committed to
OL,9,Fsupporting them where we can."
OL,11,FIt is not yet clear whether there will
OL,12,Fbe any job losses as a result of this
OL,13,Fdecision, but Constable Jehan added:
OL,14,F"We'll work closely with Serco Jersey
OL,15,FLimited as we look for opportunities
OL,16,Ffor staff who wish to join the
OL,17,FGovernment of Jersey team."
